{"tid":1233894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【請尊重】希望大家唔好忘記反一地兩檢烈士 大學生熊家俊","createTime":"2019-06-16T23:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T17:28:06.000Z","uid":69568,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"881ddd6e69b06dbd747ce204382289088a74fc0e","tid":1233894,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:24:15.000Z","msg":"2017年尾 有位浸大嘅學生 因為反對一地兩檢而殉志 雖然迴響冇今次咁大<br />\n<br />\n但每次有人提到梁生係第一位反赤化烈士 我就覺得熊同學已被遺忘 經過提點佢哋先醒返起 我對此感到萬分心痛 大家千祈唔好忘記佢嘅貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一位為香港抗共而死嘅烈士都係香港大英雄 理應極受大家尊敬<br />\n<br />\n所以在此呼籲 修正返梁生並唔係第一位因反赤化而過身嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n呢個並唔係重要嘅post 純粹作為澄清之用 如感冒犯 大家可以唔使太在意<br />\n<br />\n喺度再次感激 兩位烈士<br />\n反一地兩檢烈士 熊家俊<br />\n反逃犯條例烈士 梁凌杰<br />\n<br />\n祝安息"},{"pid":"b2c339ec821413d39a01838425f3324d7bdcfb59","tid":1233894,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"7a363d9854c857d7527dee836c588035c2855013","tid":1233894,"uid":120295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"93f0ad12d7edec3f252ad0d1e431e20050dc4208","tid":1233894,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"15e119b51652d4c01da3c5ee59835a7d045c8ba1","tid":1233894,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a46abca2dd2b47ba23da01a78b2dcaa6421524b1","tid":1233894,"uid":117059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf8a38ee222710f57c46b8191c7ac55e9d8743a","tid":1233894,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb20f2e882f33607ff72446eb0845de1a7a8f4","tid":1233894,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi